videos.description: RB Darrynton Evans pushes across the plane and scores to give the Mountaineers a 7-0 lead over the Ragin' Cajuns.
videos.headline: Appalachian State strikes first with 2-yard TD run

videos.description: QB Levi Lewis scrambles out of the pocket and finds a wide-open Elijah Mitchell, who walks into the end zone to tie the game at 7-7.
videos.headline: Louisiana-Lafayette answers with 38-yard TD pass

videos.description: Eric Garror leaves his feet and reaches over Dominique Heath to pull down a huge interception and give the ball back to the Ragin' Cajuns.
videos.headline: Louisiana-Lafayette DB climbs ladder for INT

videos.description: QB Zac Thomas gets sandwiched between two Louisiana-Lafayette defenders, but still delivers an on-target pass to Darrynton Evans to make it 17-10 Mountaineers.
videos.headline: Appalachian State QB takes hit, throws strike for TD
